OpenTelemetry Distro
====================

|pypi|

.. |pypi| image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/opentelemetry-distro.svg

Installation
------------

::

    pip install opentelemetry-distro


This package provides entrypoints to configure OpenTelemetry.
